title: Ep.25: All Time 5 on 5, Best Team In The East, Draft Sleepers, and Much More!
description: PLEASE HELP! Vote on who you think has a better 5 on 5 squad! We dive deep into our teams and are both convinced our team would dominate. We also discuss our pick for the team to come out of the east. We all know about the top draft prospects but what about the sleepers? Tune in to find out more!
